addons.description: Mandatory by law. ₹50 Lakhs coverage against accidental injury or death.
addons.description_v1: Covers death or disability of the owner-driver due to a car accident {bold}(sum insured up to ₹50 Lakhs){/bold}.
addons.description_v2: Stay legally protected with our personal accident cover add-on. In case of accidental injury or death of the car owner, receive up to Rs 15 L.

addons.description: Protect your loved ones in case of unfortunate accidents. ₹2 Lakhs coverage per passenger for 1 year against accidental injury or death.
addons.description_v1: Get protection against injury/death of the passengers with a sum insured of  {bold}₹2 Lakhs{/bold} for each passenger.
addons.description_v2: Protect your loved ones against accidental injury or death. Up to ₹2 Lakhs coverage per passenger against unfortunate accidents.

addons.description: Get yourself extra cushioning by keeping your no claim bonus intact even in the event of a claim. Applicable only for 1 claim
addons.description_v1: Retain your No Claim Bonus (NCB) even if you make a claim. Note: No claim bonus is the discount you earn for not making any insurance claims, it resets to zero when you claim.
addons.description_v2: No claim bonus is the discount you earn for driving safely without any insurance claims. It resets to zero when you claim. Add this to protect your current NCB even if you make a claim.

addons.description_v2: Protect your car driver with coverage up to ₹ 1 L in case of accidental injury or death.
